snippet.title: Jak & Daxter: The Precursor Legacy Trailer
snippet.description: An trailer from Jak & Daxter from 2001. Extracted from an unknown demo disc, one of the best platformers ever made. From the creators of the amazing Crash Bandicoot series. Music playing in this trailer Dreamcatcher - In an Ocean of Joy.
